Job Description
Responsible for providing the company's after-sales technical and services support
Provide technical expertise for required solutions
Assist in product roll-out and startup, maintain current equipment and resolve faults as required
Ensure 24x7 standby services through a rotational duty schedule
May provide support in a pre-sale through post-sale capacity
Job Requirements
Experience in UPS (Uninterruptible Power Supply) servicing, commissioning and troubleshooting
Technical background in analyzing electrical problems
Knowledge in the UPS architecture and electrical single line diagram (SLD)
Willing to work overtime and attend ad-hoc jobs or service calls
Team player Hard-working
